desc: Shock Delete Engineering (SDE) manufacturers electronic shock (MagneRide) and height simulator kits for a variety of GM, Ford and Mopar vehicles. Our kits are designed to be plug-n-play and require no custom wiring. Please contact us with questions about your application today. Proudly made in the U.S.A.
